{
  "stem": "16214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said that my father is not there-- he's dead-- and just get out of here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they just were not very helpful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is the family, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they all were just terrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one cannot blame them one way or another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother started crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the mother of-- of my-- of my father's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] mother-in-law of my father's brother came out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she says, child, don't cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your husband is fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have documents for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have documents for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you'll be fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just, you know-- just relax.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they decided there was just no way that they would be able to have-- my mother decided.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told her she wouldn't be able to go to Germany to work with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the decision was made that I should be left someplace, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And basically that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the next couple of days, my mother took me and placed me in one of these sort of-- I don't know how you say these-- these things, actually.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's just sort of like a setup where you put a kid in, and you cover the child, you know, so it won't be cold, etc.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so she put me into that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she also placed on my neck a cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she wrote a letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the letter-- perhaps she-- I think she left still a few things, whatever she had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and she wrote a letter specifying that she is in the underground, and the Germans are after her, and they most likely will catch her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she would like at least for her daughter to be alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
